rdcingest.title: Labshare Test 1
rdcingest.description: This dataset describes the baseline characteristics of a small wavetank used to test the efficiency of scale models wave power devices such as Oscillating Water Columns. The rig consists of a 4.9 metre wave tank with a paddle wheel at one end which generates propagating waves. The tank features a beach that is overtopped by the waves to prevent wave refection. This means there is a constant source of waves. The water that overtops the beach is pumped back into the tank to maintain the water level.
